<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/about.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #fff0f5;
            /* Lavender blush background */
            color: #333;
            /* Dark grey text */
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .about-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            /* White background */
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            /* Soft shadow */
        }
        
        .about-title {
            color: #ff69b4;
            /* Pink title */
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .about-content {
            color: #666;
            /* Medium grey text */
            text-align: justify;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="about-container">
        <h1 class="about-title">About Us</h1>
        <div class="about-content">
            <p>Welcome to our blog platform! This website is dedicated to providing a space where users can create, share, and discover blog posts on various topics. Whether you're a seasoned blogger or just starting out, our platform is designed to be user-friendly
                and accessible to everyone.</p>
            <p>Our mission is to foster a community of writers and readers who can engage with content that inspires, informs, and entertains. We believe that everyone has a story to tell and our platform is here to help you share yours with the world.</p>
            <p>Here are some of the features our platform offers:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Create and publish your own blog posts with ease.</li>
                <li>Edit your posts after publishing to keep your content up-to-date.</li>
                <li>Delete posts that you no longer want to be visible.</li>
                <li>Browse and read blog posts from other users.</li>
                <li>Engage with content through comments and likes (coming soon!).</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Our team is constantly working to improve the platform and add new features to enhance your blogging experience. We welcome your feedback and suggestions, so please don't hesitate to get in touch with us.</p>
            <p>Thank you for being a part of our community. Happy blogging!</p>
        </div>

    </div>
    <%- include('partials/footer.ejs') %>

</body>

</html>